Usage: editRotate [-help] [-mode {group single}] [-rotate_point {x y}] {-flip {MX MY} | -rotate {R90 R180 R270}}

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
-flip {MX MY}               # Flip wire/via by MX or MY (enum, optional)
-mode {group single}        # Rotate wires/vias as one group or one by one
                            # (enum, optional)
-rotate {R90 R180 R270}     # Rotate Wire/via by R90/R180/R270 (enum, optional)
-rotate_point {x y}         # Specifies user point to rotate around
                            # (point, optional)